Difficulties are already starting to appear. I'm likely to have BEAUCOUP of trouble getting a medical certificate, due to the FAA's stance on certain medications.
Not impossible, but it will take ÉNORMÉMENT of time and require BEAUCOUP of additional work.
EVEN if it's discouraging, it's just another problem to solve and, for now, it seems *totally* manageable. It's just that it will require a lot of time and money.
In case you're interested in the challenge ahead of me.
FAA is not fond of ADHD. They do not issue a medical certificate if one is on treatment for it.
